item.title: Why I ditched chrome for Edge?
item.description: I've been using google chrome for a long time I love the extensions and the look and feel of chrome but then I realized that all these extensions now work on the new Microsoft edge plus edge got a bunch of additional features. That I always wish chrome had let's take a look at why edge may be the better choice.
